Title: 14.2 Loadable Function Reference
Name: version_tokens_unlock()
Description:
Releases all locks that were acquired within the current
              session using
              version_tokens_lock_exclusive()
              and
              version_tokens_lock_shared().

Press CTRL+C to copy mysql> SELECT version_tokens_unlock();

| version_tokens_unlock() |
+-------------------------+
|                       1 |
